name: Gottfried Kibelka
text: Parking is an issue, Starbucks drive through creates a situation that invites people to drive on the left side of the road behind the stores. Pretty big potholes behind store front and non appetizing AC runoff. Getting in from or out onto Galleria Blvd. Almost forces traffic law violations. Lots of lanes, lots of traffic but lane markings don't allow for safe or common sense traffic flow.

name: John Fritz
text: You can't go wrong with Milo's chicken tenders.
